            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/06/19/poverty-in-the-uk-doubles-over-the-past-30-years-despite-robust-economic-growth/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Poverty in the UK Doubles Over the Past 30 Years, Despite Robust &#8220;Economic Growth&#8221;"><span>5</span> Comments</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/financialization/" rel="tag">Financialization</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/gold-standard/" rel="tag">Gold Standard</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/neo-feudalism/" rel="tag">Neo Feudalism</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/oligarchy/" rel="tag">Oligarchy</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/poverty-and-social-exclusion-project/" rel="tag">Poverty and Social Exclusion project</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/pse/" rel="tag">PSE</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/serfdom/" rel="tag">Serfdom</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/ukip/" rel="tag">UKIP</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/06/19/poverty-in-the-uk-doubles-over-the-past-30-years-despite-robust-economic-growth/#comments">5</a> 
