            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/03/29/the-co-op-movement-a-decentralized-solution-to-solving-inequality-and-avoiding-serfdom/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on The Co-Op Movement – A Decentralized Solution to Solving Inequality and Avoiding Serfdom?"><span>6</span> Comments</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/corruptions/" rel="tag">corruptions</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/crony-capitalism/" rel="tag">Crony Capitalism</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/neo-feudalism/" rel="tag">Neo Feudalism</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/new-york-times/" rel="tag">New York Times</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/oligarchy/" rel="tag">Oligarchy</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/who-needs-a-boss/" rel="tag">who needs a boss</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/03/29/the-co-op-movement-a-decentralized-solution-to-solving-inequality-and-avoiding-serfdom/#comments">8</a> 
