        <article id="post-2713" class="post-2713 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-interviews tag-brave-new-feudal-manor-houses tag-darden-restaurants tag-fsn tag-gap-stores tag-kerry-lutz tag-neo-feudalism tag-podcast clearfix rtp-post-box">
            
            <header class="post-header ">
                
                                            <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2012/12/12/interview-3-with-financial-survival-network-when-castles-grow-in-washington/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Interview #3 with Financial Survival Network:  When Castles Grow in Washington">Interview #3 with Financial Survival Network:  When Castles Grow in Washington</a></h2>
                <?php// rtp_hook_end_post_title(); ?>

                
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-top"><span class="author"><a class="fn" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/author/mkriegs/" title="Posts by Michael Krieger">Michael Krieger</a></span> <span class="rtp-meta-separator">|</span> Posted <time class="published" datetime="2012-12-12T17:50:06+00:00">Wednesday Dec 12, 2012</time> at 5:50 pm         <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2012/12/12/interview-3-with-financial-survival-network-when-castles-grow-in-washington/#respond" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Interview #3 with Financial Survival Network:  When Castles Grow in Washington">Leave a comment</a></span>
            </div><!-- .post-meta -->            </header><!-- .post-title -->

            <div class="post-content">
                                

                
                <p>Yesterday, I had the pleasure to record my third interview with Kerry Lutz of <a href="http://financialsurvivalnetwork.com/">Financial Survival Network</a>.  Kerry is a fellow freedom fighter for civil rights, the Constitution and sound money.  In this segment we discuss a wide range of topics including recent weakness in The Gap and Darden Restaurants, as well as castles being built in D.C. as a sign of American feudalism.</p>
<p>Listen <a href="http://ec.libsyn.com/p/0/0/4/004eb3839bf916df/MK12102012.mp3?d13a76d516d9dec20c3d276ce028ed5089ab1ce3dae902ea1d01cd8234d7c8583680&amp;c_id=5223407">here</a>.  Enjoy!</p>
<p>Mike</p>
